Made for my Colombian girlfriend so I could \"put her in the game\".
Also adds a basic follower named Melissa Andrea Ramirez, who can be found in the Whiterun Bannered Mare.
descriptionHtml:
Slightly over powered, most of the values are 69...
Level 1:
Health 69
Magicka 69
Stamina 69
Should auto level with character.
Made for my Colombian girlfriend so I could \"put her in the game\".
Also adds a basic follower named Melissa Andrea Ramirez, who can be found in the Whiterun Bannered Mare.
She is good(+5) at Sneak, Alchemy, Smithing, Block, Pickpocket, and extra good(+10) at Speech.
Also you find her wearing ancient nordic armor and she has in her inventory 69 ales and a flaming steel sword.
author: 5L4Y3R
